title: Hot Porn Chicken - Chicken Nut Magnet (2009) (320kbps)
description:
Hot Porn Chicken introduces you to their, and the rest of the world's, greatest album ever created. Earlier artists that used the studios include the likes of The Beatles, Robert Johnson, Son House, Aerosmith, Nickelback, Creed, Green Day, and Modest Mouse, if you're into that indie stuff. Not surprisingly, Zack stated immediately after mastering the album that this is the greatest thing his ears have ever been graced with absorbing, and anybody who doesn't listen to this album is not a human being, or at least a very gay one.

With that said, feast your listening devices upon the greatest set of organized sound ever organized. Don't forget your tissues though, because it could get messy.
